1	//! Built-in dispatch for the Saga 11 model DSL.
2	//!
3	//! `linear(in_dim, out_dim, seed)` creates a fresh `ModelSpec::Linear`
4	//! whose `W` and `b` parameters are stored in the environment under
5	//! generated names. `apply(model_ident, X)` looks up the model and
6	//! evaluates it on the given input.
